                name="Kengan Ashura"
            /> by Yabako Sandrovich
            <br /><Link
                link="https://myanimelist.net/manga/85781/Dungeon_Meshi"
                name="Dungeon Meshi"
            /> by Kui Ryouko
            <br /><Link
                link="https://myanimelist.net/manga/93753/Vanitas_no_Karte"
                name="The Case Study of Vanitas"
            /> by Mochizuki Jun
            <br /><Link
                link="https://myanimelist.net/manga/107562/Kusuriya_no_Hitorigoto"
                name="The Apothecary Diaries"
            /> by Hyuuga Natsu, Nanao Itsuki, Nekokurage
        </p>
    </Details>
    <Details name="Movies">
        <p>
            <Link
                link="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1615147/"
                name="Margin Call"
            />
            <br /><Link
                link="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt14205554/"
                name="Kpop Demon Hunters"
            />
        </p>
    </Details>
    <Details name="TV Shows">
        <p>
            <Link link="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt11126994/" name="Arcane" />
            <br /><Link
                link="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt11280740/"
                name="Severance"
            />
            <br /><Link
                link="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0412142/"
                name="House M.D."
            />
            <br /><Link
                link="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0383126/"
                name="Mythbusters"
            />
        </p>
    </Details>
    <Details name="Websites">
        <p>
            Some maybe useful websites.
            <br />
            <Link link="https://annas-archive.pk/" name="Anna's Archive:" />
            <span> Massive Digital Library</span>
            <br />
            <Link link="https://wotaku.wiki/" name="Wotaku Wiki:" />
